description: Finally a Thai gourmet food truck. Serving traditional Thai street food from bbq on sticks to pad thai and yummy thai iced tea boba! Sponsored by Tourism Authority of Thailand and also a member of Stand up to Cancer with their new campaign 'Cooking to cure cancer'. Launched October 30,2010.Thailand is labeled "paradise" not only for its breathtaking beauty and inspiring culture, but also for its culinary brilliance. From adrenaline-rush Bangkok to serene seaside towns in the South and tranquil villages located along the Mekong River, Thai cuisine is as rich and diverse as its culture. Uniquely crafted to appeal to all tastes, Thai food combines best of flavours, textures, colours and presentations. Adding this to the country's liberal supply of ancient cooking secrets and the Thai hospitality and you'll find a culinary treasure trove that offers enriching and memorable experience.
name: Streets of Thailand
